verses.text:
All we like sheep have gone astray, have gone astray, have gone astray;
All we like sheep have gone astray, turned every one to his own way;
And the Lord hath laid on him the iniquity of us all,
And the Lord hath laid on him the iniquity of us all.

We have all gone astray from the path of the right, the path of the right;
We have all gone astray from the path of the right, turned every one to his own way;
And the Lord hath laid on him the iniquity of us all,
And the Lord hath laid on him the iniquity of us all.

But Christ the Lord died for us all, died for us all, died for us all;
But Christ the Lord died for us all, turned every one to his own way;
And the Lord hath laid on him the iniquity of us all,
And the Lord hath laid on him the iniquity of us all.
